reviewText:
Experience + Reaction = Outcome.  What I love about this book is that this information should be common sense.  You hear it, and you think "DUH!" Yet it's not how we are living our lives.  Jack reminds us, in plain terms, that we hold the reins in our own lives.  If we don't like an aspect of our lives, we have the power to change it!  And he tells us how to do it.  Whether you struggle with personal relationships, weight, finances, your job, your kids or your happiness; all are within your power to change.

It's a must read, truly.
I'M RECOMENDING TO EVERY ONE TO HAVE JACK CONFIELD COLLECTIONS. HIS REAL AND HIS GENIUSES IN TEACHING.

I really like Jack's candid presentation and he has an endearing personality. Jack Canfield offer's a wealth of information in this DVD presentation.  He also offer's many practical ways to accomplish the priniciples mentioned.  This is definitely a product I recommend.
Doug

It started by me purchasing the book. Then, the audio book and finally the DVD Just could not have enough of the material covered in the Success Principles. The advises provided have been great source of success for me. Dr. Israel King, Ph D, Author of How To Keep A Man
